	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=96267><span id= >HisRoyalPhatness</span></a><br><span id=notbold>116 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Good [4.00]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>Don't get too down the lvls do come eventually.&nbsp;&nbsp;I was in 30 for over a month, 35 for like 6 weeks and I'm almost at the end of month 2 for 40.  Just be glad they got rid of hell lvls.  If you just keep your head up, and look for groups you can still rake in some cash too.  Go to Rathe Mountains, get a group, you can pull in somewhere in the range of 100pp in an hour with a good group, and some nice exp along with it.  Plus druids with high wis can single kite giants almost constantly after 40, and quad kite em with no problem after 45.  One of my friends (lvl 50 druid) made 7k pp in about 7 hours.  So just stick with it it all gets better eventually.</p>&nbsp;<br><span class=sm>----------------------------</span><br>Lvl 50 Arrowflinger of Tunare &lt;Clan Ice Claw&gt; Mith Marr Server</td></tr>
